  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a proof-of-concept study with a prospective observational design, where the&#xD;
      association between progressive levels of verticalization and cerebral blood flow velocity&#xD;
      (Ultrasound) in subacute stroke patients and healthy subjects will be investigated.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
